{% comment %}
  Product Info Panel - Title, Rating, Description, Price
  
  Converts React product info to Shopify Liquid
  Source: ProductDetails.tsx (lines 221-261)
  
  Features:
  - Brand/Vendor display
  - Product title
  - Star rating display
  - Review count
  - Product description
  - Price with compare-at price
  - Discount percentage badge
  
  Usage:
  {% render 'product-info-panel', product: product %}
{% endcomment %}

<div class="space-y-6">
  {%- comment -%} Product Title & Rating {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="mb-4">
    {%- comment -%} Brand/Vendor {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- if product.vendor != blank -%}
      <p class="text-[10px] text-muted-foreground tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2">
        {{ product.vendor }}
      </p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- comment -%} Product Title {%- endcomment -%}
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-3">
      {{ product.title }}
    </h1>

    {%- comment -%} Rating & Reviews {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- if product.metafields.reviews.rating != blank -%}
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
        {%- comment -%} Star Rating Display {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
          {%- assign rating = product.metafields.reviews.rating | times: 1.0 -%}
          {%- assign full_stars = rating | floor -%}
          {%- assign empty_stars = 5 | minus: full_stars -%}
          
          {%- comment -%} Full stars {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- for i in (1..full_stars) -%}
            <span class="text-yellow-500">★</span>
          {%- endfor -%}
          
          {%- comment -%} Empty stars {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- for i in (1..empty_stars) -%}
            <span class="text-gray-300">★</span>
          {%- endfor -%}
          
          {%- comment -%} Rating number {%- endcomment -%}
          <span class="ml-1 font-semibold">{{ rating | round: 1 }}</span>
        </div>

        {%- comment -%} Review count {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- if product.metafields.reviews.count != blank -%}
          <span class="text-muted-foreground">
            {{ product.metafields.reviews.count | default: 0 }} reviews
          </span>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} Product Description {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if product.description != blank -%}
    <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
      {{ product.description | strip_html | truncatewords: 50 }}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- comment -%} Price Section {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
    {%- comment -%} Current Price {%- endcomment -%}
    <span class="font-display text-3xl" id="product-price">
      {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }}
    </span>

    {%- comment -%} Compare At Price (Original Price) {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- if product.selected_or_first_available_variant.compare_at_price > product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price -%}
      <span class="text-lg text-muted-foreground line-through">
        {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.compare_at_price | money }}
      </span>

      {%- comment -%} Discount Percentage Badge {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- assign savings = product.selected_or_first_available_variant.compare_at_price | minus: product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price -%}
      {%- assign percentage = savings | times: 100.0 | divided_by: product.selected_or_first_available_variant.compare_at_price | round -%}
      <span class="badge-accent text-[10px]">
        -{{ percentage }}% OFF
      </span>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</div>

{% comment %}
  CONVERSION NOTES:
  
  React → Liquid Mappings:
  - product.brand → {{ product.vendor }}
  - product.name → {{ product.title }}
  - product.description → {{ product.description }}
  - product.price → {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }}
  - product.originalPrice → {{ product.compare_at_price | money }}
  - product.rating → {{ product.metafields.reviews.rating }}
  - product.reviews → {{ product.metafields.reviews.count }}
  
  Shopify Features Used:
  - {{ product.vendor }} - Brand name
  - {{ product.title }} - Product name
  - {{ product.description }} - Product description
  - {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant }} - Active variant
  - .price | money - Shopify money filter for currency formatting
  - .compare_at_price - Original price for discount display
  - product.metafields - Custom fields for ratings
  
  Required Metafields Setup:
  To display ratings, add these metafields to your products:
  1. reviews.rating (number_decimal) - e.g., 4.5
  2. reviews.count (number_integer) - e.g., 1381
  
  Optional Enhancements:
  1. Integrate with Shopify Reviews app
  2. Add product rating schema markup for SEO
  3. Link to reviews section on page
  4. Add social proof (e.g., "X people viewing this")
  5. Show stock availability
{% endcomment %}
